[2026-03-10T23:03:20Z] [llm] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01LRhRDtzPVz6KNC4EUbKwVY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nImplemented agent step support for host workflows with the same configuration syntax as container workflows.\n\n### Changes\n\n**`internal/host/executor.go`** — Added `executeAgent()` method and `AgentCommands`/`AgentArgs` fields to `Executor`:\n- Creates a `prompt.Adapter` with workflow-level agent commands/args\n- Supports step-level `agent_command` and `agent_args` overrides (same as container workflows)\n- Supports fallback chains (comma-separated commands)\n- Passes previous step output as user prompt via `prompt.txt`\n- Supports `prompt_step` config for explicit prompt sourcing\n- Copies adapter output to executor's output directory for downstream steps\n\n**`internal/host/runner.go`** — Reads `host.agent_command` and `host.agent_args` from workflow config and passes them to the executor.\n\n**`internal/domain/workflow.go`** — Added `host.` prefix to allowed step config key prefixes (alongside `container.`).\n\n**`.cloche/host.cloche`** — Added `host { agent_command = \"claude\" }` config block as proof of concept.\n\n### Tests added (all pass)\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_Success` — Basic agent step execution\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_Failure` — Agent failure via result marker\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_WorkflowLevelCommand` — Workflow-level agent config\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_StepLevelOverridesWorkflow` — Step overrides workflow config\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_FallbackChain` — Comma-separated fallback chain\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_PrevOutput` — Previous step output as user prompt\n- `TestExecutor_AgentStep_PromptStep` — Explicit prompt_step config\n- `TestEngine_HostWorkflow_WithAgentStep` — End-to-end workflow with agent step\n- `TestRunner_HostWorkflow_AgentStep` — Full runner with parsed host.cloche\n- `TestRunner_HostWorkflow_AgentStepOverrides